## 🔒 Security Checklist

- [ ] Keep Google Sheet private (only you have edit access)
- [ ] Set Apps Script to execute as "Me" (not as user)
- [ ] Add CORS restrictions if needed
- [ ] Enable 2FA on your Google account
- [ ] Regularly export Sheet data as backup

---

## 🌍 Language Support

The app supports Arabic (RTL) and English (LTR).

- Default: **Arabic**
- Language is saved in `localStorage`
- Switch via navbar AR/EN buttons

