## 🎨 Customization

### Change Colors
In `index.html`, find `:root { ... }` and update:
```css
--accent: #C8A45D;          /* Gold accent — change to your brand color */
--accent-blue: #3B82F6;     /* Blue accent */
```

### Add Services
Find the `.services-grid-featured` section and add/modify cards.

### Change Pricing
Find the `.pricing-grid` section and update prices.

